## Platform Icons

| Platform | Library | Never Use |
|----------|---------|-----------|
| iOS | SF Symbols (`expo-symbols`) | Icon fonts, PNGs, emoji |
| Android | Material Icons (`@expo/vector-icons/MaterialIcons`) | Icon fonts, emoji |
| Web | `lucide-react` | Emoji |

