## Animations: Spring Physics

All platforms use spring-based motion. Never use linear or basic ease curves for interactive elements.

| Use Case | Spring Config (damping/stiffness) |
|----------|-----------------------------------|
| Button feedback | 20 / 300 |
| Card expand | 12 / 180 |
| Sheet/page transition | 18 / 120–200 |
| Default | 15 / 150 |

**Mobile:** `react-native-reanimated` with `withSpring()`
**Web:** `cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)` or similar spring curves

